nbsp;<\/span><\/h3>\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">9. Governing Law<\/span><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"3525\" data-end=\"3614\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">These Terms and Conditions shall be governed in accordance with the laws of <strong data-start=\"3601\" data-end=\"3613\">Barbados<\/strong>.<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3525\" data-end=\"3614\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3621\" data-end=\"3731\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong data-start=\"3621\" data-end=\"3636\">&nbsp;<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3621\" data-end=\"3731\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong data-start=\"3621\" data-end=\"3636\">Contact Us:<\/strong><\/span><br data-start=\"3636\" data-end=\"3639\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">For questions, please contact us at:<\/span><br data-start=\"3675\" data-end=\"3678\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"\ud83d\udce7\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/17.0.2\/svg\/1f4e7.svg\">&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #ffffff;\" href=\"mailto:holiday@forrentbarbados.com\">holiday@forrentbarbados.com<\/a><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">&nbsp;| <img decoding=\"async\" draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\"\ud83d\udcde\" src=\"https:\/\/s.w.org\/images\/core\/emoji\/17.0.2\/svg\/1f4de.svg\">&nbsp;<\/span><span style=\"font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">+1 (246) 247-2229<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Terms &amp; Conditions Effective Date: March 1, 2025Company Name:&nbsp;For Rent Barbados | Inspired Real Estate Ltd. Welcome to our website. These Terms and Conditions govern your use of our website and renta